description: Searches for tasks that match the specified filter values.

parameters.name: filters
parameters.description: Array of SearchQuantumTasksFilter objects. (dict) --- A filter to use to search for tasks. The name of the device used for the task. An operator to use in the filter. The values to use for the filter. (string) ---

nested_params.name: name
nested_params.description: The name of the device used for the task.

nested_params.name: operator
nested_params.description: An operator to use in the filter.

nested_params.name: values
nested_params.description: The values to use for the filter.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A token used for pagination of results, or null if there are no additional results. Use the token value in a subsequent request to continue results where the previous request ended.

nested_items.name: quantumTasks
nested_items.description: An array of QuantumTaskSummary objects for tasks that match the specified filters.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The time at which the task was created.

nested_items.name: deviceArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the device the task ran on.

nested_items.name: endedAt
nested_items.description: The time at which the task finished.

nested_items.name: outputS3Bucket
nested_items.description: The S3 bucket where the task result file is stored..

nested_items.name: outputS3Directory
nested_items.description: The folder in the S3 bucket where the task result file is stored.

nested_items.name: shots
nested_items.description: The shots used for the task.
